    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Stoles used for the Christian sacrament of confession, purple in color; may be shorter and narrower than stoles that are used with the chasuble and intended for masses, funerals, and other rituals.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
